These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different pets are kept: pony, cat
House: wooden, tower
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, daffodil
City: marseilles, colone
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
2. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
3. the tower house is the owner of the pony##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Pet      | pony  | cat   |
| House   | tower     | wooden   |
| Flower         | daffodil | dahlia |
| City     | marseilles | colone    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, december
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, swisher
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, american
City: venice, edinburgh
1. the american is in an odd position##4
2. the oliveros-smoker is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Birthday          | november     | december |
| Cigar   | swisher | oliveros  |
| Nationality           | american         | argentine     |
| City     | venice   | edinburgh    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
