City: london, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the game-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Cigar    | chaman     | game |
