2 different pets are kept: pony, bird
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, purple
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, begonia
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the russian##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
