.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, disco
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, singing
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, banana
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport      | basketball | water-polo       |
| Music-Genre           | disco      | dubstep     |
| Hobby   | singing       | hiking   |
| Food           | banana          | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep
House: tower, art-deco
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the roller is the fan of d&b##1
4. the tower house is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Transport           | roller | quad-bike    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | dubstep |
| House           | tower         | art-deco    |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks    | fishing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-7::.
