2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Hobby      | skydiving    | magic-tricks   |
| Music-Genre          | salsa     | house |
| Nationality           | argentine | pakistani     |
| Sport   | skiing       | ice-hockey     |

