.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, drawing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, ambient
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
2. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
4. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Transport           | snowmobile | motorbike |
| Color   | fuchsia    | ivory      |
| Hobby           | sudoku      | drawing          |
| Music-Genre         | ambient | techno       |

