.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, october
City: colone, new-york
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, cucumber
2 different games are played: chess, snooker
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
3. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Birthday    | april | october    |
| City         | new-york        | colone |
| Food         | pineapple          | cucumber     |
| Game   | chess        | snooker     |

 